full_text:
Although I realize your question was for Frank, I believe the other fine developers and the folks who attended the QM event would take exception to being characterized as people who can&#39;t be honest. But it was nice to see how the audience and other presenters cheered loudly when Frank was introduced. Frank&#39;s work also was constantly considered to be one of the most influential of modern day ITC.

